# Dev planning artifacts
dev/completed/
dev/active/
dev/scratch/

# One-shot codex/claude prompts and transcripts. Structured plan dirs (with
# BRIEF.md, named-feature subfolders) and audit conclusions are committed
# explicitly — see the negation below. Loose dev/codex-* one-shots, raw .txt
# transcripts, and ad-hoc debug notes are scratch work and don't belong in
# the repo. .claude/codex-prompts/ is local-only prompt scratchpad.
dev/codex-*
!dev/codex-dev-audit-*.output.md
dev/build-failure-context.md
*.output.txt
.claude/codex-prompts/

# Playwright per-run output (artifacts, traces, videos)
test-results/
web/e2e/.output/

